Vocational Education and Training Loan Scheme. The Vocational Education and Training Loan Scheme provides financial assistance to youth of the target group to enhance their skills & employability.

Eligibility:
{'eligibility_criteria': 'The person should be from the target group of NSKFDC and have secured admission in a course run or supported by a Ministry, Department, or Organization of the Government.', 'course_eligibility': 'Vocational Education and training courses of the duration of a minimum 6 months and up to 2 years', 'age_eligibility': 'The candidate should attain a minimum age of 18 years on completion of the course and the upper age limit is up to 50 years'}

Benefits:
{'quantum_of_loan': 'Up to 90% of expenses, subject to a ceiling of Rs. 4,00,000/- for courses of duration up to 2 years', 'interest': '4% per annum, with an interest rebate of 0.5% for women', 'repayment': 'Up to 7 years'}
